---
import {
  H2C,
  H3C,
  Paragraph,
  TextWithLine,
} from '@components/atoms/index.astro'

const { customClass = '' } = Astro.props
---

<header class=`${customClass}`>
  <div
    class='rounded-full w-40 h-40 sm:w-60 sm:h-60 max-w-xs max-h-xs overflow-hidden mx-auto blur-sm hover:blur-none hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105'
  >
    <img class='w-full h-full object-cover' src='/imgs/persona.jpg' alt='' />
  </div>
  <div>
    <div class='max-w-max mx-auto'>
      <H3C customClass='relative text-start w-max'>
        <TextWithLine name='OMAR BARROS' customClass='border-[#333333]' />
      </H3C>
      <H2C customClass='text-blue-600 w-max m-auto'>INGENIERO DE SISTEMAS</H2C>
      <H2C customClass='text-blue-600 w-max m-auto'>DESARROLLADOR WEB</H2C>
    </div>

    <Paragraph customClass='max-w-lg my-2'>
      Uniendo talento técnico, espíritu innovador y dedicación: construyendo
      experiencias web excepcionales que impulsan el éxito
    </Paragraph>
  </div>

  <slot />
</header>